remarks.summary: On Friday, 2 February: Strike at 15 transport operators
remarks.text: In Berlin at BVG from approx. 3 a.m. to 10 a.m., in Brandenburg all day. This affects underground trains, trams and buses. Long-distance and regional trains as well as S-Bahn trains will run as scheduled. Info: www.vbb.de/streik and www.bvg.de

remarks.summary: .Strike at BVG
remarks.text: Friday between 3 and 10 am. U-Bahn, tram and most bus services will not run. Please select only S-Bahn Trains and "Regio" in the app or website to find alternative S-Bahn and regional services. The BVG will run again from 10 a.m., but there may still be cancellations until 12 a.m. Running services have real-time info (+ or - minutes). Weitere Informationen
